Ability.Name: Firaxian Shark Repellent
Ability.Description: A sprayable repellent for Firaxian Sharks. Can be used on allies or enemies, with differing effects. Enemy Target: Spray repellent into the eyes of a nearby opponent, ignoring the strongly worded warning label. Momentarily stuns the opponent, and blinds them for 9s. Friendly Target: Spray repellent on an ally. Reduces the aggro range of Firaxian Sharks within 50m by 80%. Upon taking damage from a Firaxian Shark, reduces threat against that attacker by 80%. Effects last 4h.

Ability.Name: Ground Pound
Ability.Description: Your creature slams into an enemy hitting all hostiles 4m around the enemy target dealing <<1>> kinetic damage to up to 5 targets.

Ability.Name: Crushing Bite
Ability.Description: Your creature sensing the target's weakend state goes in for a big bite, dealing <<1>> internal damage. Can only be used on targets with less than 30% health.

Ability.Name: Stunning Slam
Ability.Description: Your creature slams the ground to stun the target for 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Vicious Kick
Ability.Description: Your creature kicks the target dealing <<1>> internal damage and causes the target to become immobilized.

Ability.Name: Cutting Clobber
Ability.Description: Your creature cuts the target by dealing <<1>> internal damage over a 10 second duration.

Ability.Name: Kolto Collar Scan
Ability.Description: Your creature uses its Kolto Collar to heal a friendly target for <<1>> over 3 seconds.

Ability.Name: Kolto Collar Dart
Ability.Description: Your creature fires a Kolto Dart from its collar, healing the target for <<1>>.

Ability.Name: Soothing Spittle
Ability.Description: Your creature projects special digestive juices on the target healing for <<1>> and cleansing it of mental and physical effects over 9 seconds. What an incredible smell!

Ability.Name: Hypnotizing Cry
Ability.Description: Your creature unleashes a mighty cry that dazes the target for up to 8 seconds. Damage to the target causes this effect to end prematurely. Targets may only be affected by Hypnotizing Cry once every 30 seconds. Target must not be suffering from periodic damage and have greater than 90% max health.

Ability.Name: Collar Kolto Shield
Ability.Description: Your creature uses its collar to place a Kolto-powered shield around the target, preventing a moderate amount of damage for up to 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Overcharge Collar
Ability.Description: Your creature's collar overcharges unleashing an electric discharge dealing <<1>> internal damage to up to 5 enemies 5m around the impact. Generates a moderate amount of threat and reduces incoming damage by 50% for 10 seconds. Does not hit sleeping, lifted, or incapacitated enemies.

Ability.Name: Tongue Pull
Ability.Description: Your three-tongued ginx lets loose its genetically modified tongues and pulls the closest three targets while generating a high amount of threat. Cannot be used on targets in cover or on targets with Boss Immunity.

Ability.Name: Riveting Taunt
Ability.Description: Your creature taunts attacking enemies forcing them to attack your creature and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Draining Attack
Ability.Description: Your creature attacks the target and delivers a powerful attack, dealing <<1>> weapon damage, heals for 25% of damage dealt and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Personal Barb
Ability.Description: Taunts the target, forcing it to attack your creature for 6 seconds. Also reinforces your creature by placing an absorb shield that absorbs a moderate amount of damage.
